headline.print_headline: Merkel Says Will Push for Ceasefire on Ukraine Visit
headline.main: Merkel Says Will Push for Ceasefire on Ukraine Visit

lead_paragraph: German Chancellor Angela Merkel said the main goal of her trip to Ukraine on Saturday was to help secure a ceasefire, reiterating that there could be no military solution to the crisis.
